snippet.title: Toadette Strikes: Toad Strikes Back 2 Part #1
snippet.description:
Hello, everyone. I have decided to play a game created by Thunder Dragon called Toadette Strikes: Toad Strikes Back 2. Since Toad and Toadette are some of my favorite characters, I decided to give this game a whirl. I really enjoyed every second of the game. Colorful levels, nice music, and many different characters you can talk to.

Story: In the future, a sleeping spell has affected the Toads everywhere and Kammy the Magikoopa takes responsibility for it. She commands the Koopa Klan to take the kidnap the Toads for her evil purposes. However, one female Toad, inspired by the legends of Super Mario, decided to take action and break the curse!

The fan-game is made by Thunder Dragon and Toadette belongs to Nintendo.

Download: http://www.mfgg.net/?act=resdb&param=02&c=2&id=30718

Note: For any Mushroom Medal that I missed after completing a level, there will be a clip at the end of the level or something similar to it to showcase it's location.
